#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:32
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"FAI rules, allows only FAI start, finish and turn point types, for badges "
"and records. Enables FAI finish height for final glide calculation."
msgstr ""
"FAI pravila, dopušta samo FAI početak, završetak i kretanja točaka za "
"atribute i povijest. Ograničenja FAI završni visina za finalnu glidanju."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:34
#, no-c-format
msgid "FAI rules, path from a start to two turn points and return."
msgstr "FAI pravila, put od početka do dva kretanja točke i povrat."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:35
#, no-c-format
msgid "FAI rules, path from start to a single turn point and return."
msgstr "FAI pravila, put od početka do jedne kretanja točke i povrat."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:36
#, no-c-format
msgid "FAI rules, path from start to a goal destination."
msgstr "FAI pravila, put od početka do cilja destinacije."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:37
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Racing task around turn points. Can also be used for FAI badge and record "
"tasks. Allows all shapes of observation zones."
msgstr ""
"Takmičenje oko kretanja točaka. Može se koristiti i za atribute i povijest "
"FAI. Ograničenja zone za pregled."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:39
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Task through assigned areas, minimum task time applies. Restricted to "
"cylinder and sector observation zones."
msgstr ""
"Zadatak kroz pridružene oblasti, minimalna zadatkova vrijeme se primjenjuje."
" Ograničenja na cilindrične i sektorne zone za pregled."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:41
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Modified area task. Task with start, finish and at least one predefined 1 "
"mile cylinder. Pilot can add additional points as needed. Minimum task time "
"applies."
msgstr ""
"Modifikovan zona zadataka. Zadatak sa početkom, završetkom i barem jednim "
"predviđenim cilindrom od 1 milja. Piloti može dodati dodatne točke ako je "
"potrebno. Minimalna zadatkova vrijeme se primjenjuje."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:42
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Racing task with a mix of assigned areas and turn points, minimum task time "
"applies."
msgstr ""
"Razigravački zadatak sa kombinacijom određenih područja i tačaka za "
"kretanje, minimalna trajanje zadatka se primjenjuje."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:43
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Casual touring task, uses start and finish cylinders and FAI sector turn "
"points."
msgstr ""
"Razgovorni zadatak, koristi start i završni cilindri i FAI sektor tačke za "
"kretanje."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:56
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A 90-degree sector with 1 km radius. Cross corner edge from inside area to "
"start."
msgstr "Sektor od 90° s promjerom 1 km. Prelazak u početak izvan područja."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:57
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A straight line start gate. Cross start gate from inside area to start."
msgstr ""
"Prava linijska startna stanica. Prelazak startne stanice izvan područja do "
"početa."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:58
#, no-c-format
msgid "A cylinder. Exit area to start."
msgstr "Cilindar. Izlaz područje do početa."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:59
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A 90-degree sector with 'infinite' length sides. Cross any edge, scored from"
" corner point."
msgstr ""
"Sektor od 90° s 'infinite' dužinama. Prelazak na bilo koji rub, osmislen od "
"tačke u kutu."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:61
#, no-c-format
msgid "A keyhole. Scored from center."
msgstr "Kvadratni segment. Osmislen od centra."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:62
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"(German rules) Any point within 1/2 km of center or 10 km of a 90-degree "
"sector. Scored from center."
msgstr ""
"(Nemački pravila)  Ova tačka se nalazi u okviru 1/2 km od centra ili 10 km "
"od 90° sektor. Osmislen od centra."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"(British rules) Any point within 1/2 km of center or 20 km of a 90-degree "
"sector. Scored from center."
msgstr ""
"(Britanska pravila) Ova tačka se nalazi u okviru 1/2 km od centra ili 20 km "
"od 90° sektor. Osmislen od centra."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:66
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"(British rules) Any point within 1/2 km of center or 10 km of a 180-degree "
"sector. Scored from center."
msgstr ""
"(Britanska pravila) Ova tačka se nalazi u okviru 1/2 km od centra ili 10 km "
"od 180° sektor. Osmislen od centra."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "A cylinder. Any point within area scored from center."
msgstr "Cilindar. Ova tačka se nalazi u okviru područja osmislena od centra."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "A 1 mile cylinder. Scored by farthest point reached in area."
msgstr "Cilindar od 1 milja. Osmislen od najudaljenijih točaka u području."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:70
#, no-c-format
msgid "A cylinder. Scored by farthest point reached in area."
msgstr "Cilindar. Osmislen od najudaljenijih točaka u području."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A sector that can vary in angle and radius. Scored by farthest point reached"
" inside area."
msgstr ""
"Sektor koji može se mijenjati u uglu i promjeru. Osmislen od najudaljenijih "
"točaka u području."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:73
#, no-c-format
msgid "A 90-degree sector with 1 km radius. Cross edge to finish."
msgstr "Sektor od 90° s promjerom 1 km. Prelazak na rub do završetka."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cross finish gate line into area to finish."
msgstr "Prethodna granica za prekid u prostoru za završavanje."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:75
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enter cylinder to finish."
msgstr "Vremenska cilindrica za prekid."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:76
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A 180-degree sector with 5 km radius. Exit area in any direction to start."
msgstr ""
"Sektor od 180° s promjerom 5 km. Izlazak iz okružja u bilo koji smjer da "
"započne."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A sector that can vary in angle, inner and outer radius. Scored by farthest "
"point reached inside area."
msgstr ""
"Sektor koji može varijrati u uglu, unaprijed i vanjski promjer. Skori se "
"najdalje udaljeno mesto u prostoru."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "A symmetric quadrant with a custom radius."
msgstr "Simetrična kvart za custom promjer."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:80
#, no-c-format
msgid "A keyhole. Scored by farthest point reached in area."
msgstr "Kviz-forma. Skori se najdalje udaljeno mesto u prostoru."

